title.en: Onnanoko ga Ochita Saki wa, Ore no Musuko no Sakippo deshita

description.en: My only happiness in my old homestead is in my imagination, reminiscing of the young and beautiful landlord. Then one day ... I went upstairs to complain about the unbearable noise upstairs, but I see that it is a very beautiful girl and forgive it. That night I'm masturbating while I think about the girl upstairs then, with a roar, the ceiling collapses and she falls on my dick!
